ptrace system call wrapper for Ruby.
====================================

Author: Koichi Sasada
Create Date: Wed Sep 17 04:19:52 2008

NOTES ON THIS FORK:
- reorganised into a gem (but not pushed to rubygems yet)
- tested on Linux (Debian Squeeze 2.6.32-5-686 #1 SMP Mon Jun 13 04:13:06 UTC
  2011 i686 GNU/Linux)
- to build and test, run
    rake ext
  to build the extension, and then run
    rake test
- to make a gem file to install, type
  rake build
